00:03:16.430 --> 00:03:17.270
You...

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.870
How dare you threaten me with your child?

00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:21.120
That's right.

00:03:22.150 --> 00:03:23.150
If not for the child,

00:03:23.150 --> 00:03:24.710
