00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:25.560
General,

00:07:26.600 --> 00:07:27.870
do you remember what Qin Ruoyi

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:29.480
said to Scholar Kong?

00:07:31.310 --> 00:07:32.240
